Comparing with the pearson model

Filter out low-count domains.

isRobustDomain <- function(d) {
  return (d > 2)
}
robust_coef_names <- names(Filter(isRobustDomain, domainSizes))
robust_coefs <- coefs[robust_coef_names,]
